    <div class="label">History</div>
    <div class="columns">
      <p>
        In my teens I self-studied 3D animation under the foolish belief that I'd enjoy a career as a <em>computer artist</em>.
        But just as art school was about to ruin my life for the wrong muse,
        I realized my joy was for the technology, not the imagery.
      </p>
      <p>
